---
title: Herby Chicken & Hummus Sauce with Garlic Rice & Cucumber Salad
description: This meal is all Mediterranean vibes, with spiced chicken and garlicky rice dressed in a fresh and tasty yoghurt
hummus. Accompanied by a crunchy cucumber salad, every bite is a passport to sunny shores and savoury delights!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
